{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"611145a8a9","title":"黑格尔——恩格斯学派的宣言","origin":"北京大学社会主义思想教育委员会编印《北京大学右派分子反动言论汇集》，一九五七年十月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e6d3120f68","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":31,"articleId":"611145a8a9"}],"tags":[{"id":"5bfa9ca15d","name":"宣言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"19f3f1b8ea","name":"北京大学"},{"id":"69f88dd417","name":"百花学社"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"826eddcaaf","type":"title","text":"黑格尔——恩格斯学派的宣言","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"611145a8a9"},{"id":"f748093bce","type":"authors","text":"北京大学百花学社","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"611145a8a9"},{"id":"1a59db9df9","type":"subtitle","text":"（现已改名为百花学社， 1957．5．31晚）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"611145a8a9"},{"id":"355c69be73","type":"paragraph","text":"一、拥护社会主义公有制，拥护党，拥护毛主席，拥护百花齐放的方针。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"611145a8a9"},{"id":"4eb3f8e8f2","type":"paragraph","text":"二、要求扩大社会主义民主要求健全社会主义法制？要求青年人像青年人那样生活，反对“三害”反对限制思惟的恶劣倾向。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"611145a8a9"},{"id":"ef1f362c98","type":"paragraph","text":"三、百花学社是一个学术性团体，以学术讨论为其主要活动内容，通过学术性刊物，讨论会及青年所喜爱的方式发表各种意见。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"611145a8a9"},{"id":"5cd2d2cd34","type":"paragraph","text":"四、凡本校同学皆可入社，有随时退社的自由，本社没有纪律，学社不对社员言行负责。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"611145a8a9"},{"id":"503cbb3ae4","type":"paragraph","text":"五、本社发起者黑格尔——恩格斯学派是百花学社的一派，百花中的一朵，该学派不对学社的言行负责，学社也不对学派的言行负责。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"611145a8a9"}],"page":{"id":"550b25d671","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"611145a8a9","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}